<paragraph blockId="38.[178,1085,1096,1205]" pageId="38" pageNumber="1695">
Black. Pale yellow: the whole of clypeus but semitransparent ventral edge; subapical 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[178,217,1125,1147]" pageId="38" pageNumber="1695">Tsa</emphasis>
; apical palpi; two narrow subapical stripes on 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[710,736,1125,1149]" pageId="38" pageNumber="1695">
N 
<subScript attach="left" box="[728,736,1135,1149]" fontSize="6" pageId="38" pageNumber="1695">1</subScript>
</emphasis>
disk; half tegula; most of 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1018,1078,1125,1149]" pageId="38" pageNumber="1695">
LaSt 
<subScript attach="left" box="[1070,1078,1135,1149]" fontSize="6" pageId="38" pageNumber="1695">2</subScript>
</emphasis>
; ventral surface of 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[362,389,1154,1178]" pageId="38" pageNumber="1695">
X 
<subScript attach="right" box="[381,389,1164,1178]" fontSize="6" pageId="38" pageNumber="1695">1</subScript>
</emphasis>
, spots on 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[492,518,1154,1178]" pageId="38" pageNumber="1695">
X 
<subScript attach="left" box="[510,518,1164,1178]" fontSize="6" pageId="38" pageNumber="1695">2</subScript>
</emphasis>
and 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[566,592,1154,1178]" pageId="38" pageNumber="1695">
X 
<subScript attach="left" box="[584,592,1164,1178]" fontSize="6" pageId="38" pageNumber="1695">3</subScript>
</emphasis>
; most of legs; very narrow apical stripe on 1 
<superScript attach="left" box="[1048,1059,1148,1162]" fontSize="6" pageId="38" pageNumber="1695">st</superScript>
to 5 
<superScript attach="left" box="[191,203,1177,1191]" fontSize="6" pageId="38" pageNumber="1695">th</superScript>
terga. and last metamerus are brown. Wings hyaline.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="38.[178,1085,1221,1389]" pageId="38" pageNumber="1695">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[178,226,1221,1243]" pageId="38" pageNumber="1695">PoG</emphasis>
area depressed. Mid flagellomeri with a ratio 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[733,750,1221,1243]" pageId="38" pageNumber="1695">L</emphasis>
/ 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[757,792,1221,1243]" pageId="38" pageNumber="1695">LA</emphasis>
mor than 2.4. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[959,1005,1221,1245]" pageId="38" pageNumber="1695">
Em 
<subScript attach="left" box="[997,1005,1231,1245]" fontSize="6" pageId="38" pageNumber="1695">3</subScript>
</emphasis>
mostly wrinkled. Fore border of 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[452,478,1250,1274]" pageId="38" pageNumber="1695">
N 
<subScript attach="left" box="[470,478,1260,1274]" fontSize="6" pageId="38" pageNumber="1695">1</subScript>
</emphasis>
disk bluntly angled but medially where a line of carina exists; only blunt prominence on its anteroventral corner; ratio 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[860,918,1279,1303]" pageId="38" pageNumber="1695">
<subScript attach="left" box="[860,918,1279,1303]" fontSize="6" pageId="38" pageNumber="1695">LApos</subScript>
</emphasis>
/ 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[925,971,1279,1303]" pageId="38" pageNumber="1695">
<subScript attach="left" box="[925,971,1279,1303]" fontSize="6" pageId="38" pageNumber="1695">Lmed</subScript>
</emphasis>
about 2.5. Hind femur simple. Apical surface of 1 
<superScript attach="left" box="[606,617,1303,1317]" fontSize="6" pageId="38" pageNumber="1695">st</superScript>
sternum smooth and 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[856,870,1308,1330]" pageId="38" pageNumber="1695">p</emphasis>
-less. Tergal surface without secondary 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[376,390,1338,1360]" pageId="38" pageNumber="1695">p</emphasis>
. Last tergum noticeably tapering apically, with distinct epipygium by lateral carinae; very shallow median notch.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="38.[178,851,1404,1426]" box="[178,851,1404,1426]" pageId="38" pageNumber="1695">N o t e. Small species with angled volsella and tapered aedeagus.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="38.[178,904,1442,1464]" box="[178,904,1442,1464]" pageId="38" pageNumber="1695">Derivatio nominis. From the name of the people inhabiting SW Africa.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="38.[178,353,1479,1501]" box="[178,353,1479,1501]" pageId="38" pageNumber="1695">Female unknown</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
